---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
import Header from '../components/Header.astro';
import Footer from '../components/Footer.astro';
import { siteConfig, cabinFacts } from '../config/site';
---

<BaseLayout title="About Bush Baby | Story, Host, and What to Expect" description="Learn the story behind Bush Baby and what makes this private Sabie cabin a warm, trusted nature escape." canonicalPath="/about">
  <Header />
  <main>
    <section class="page-hero" style={`--hero:url(${siteConfig.assets.aboutHero})`}>
      <div class="container"><h1>About Bush Baby</h1><p>A warm, sincere space built around privacy, comfort, and care.</p></div>
    </section>

    <section class="section"><div class="container narrow"><h2>Our Story</h2><p>Bush Baby began as a shared dream between host and husband: to create a peaceful place where guests could rest, reconnect, and enjoy Sabie’s natural beauty. After his passing, that dream continues with the same heart, now carried forward with care, gratitude, and personal attention to each enquiry.</p><p>This is not a large, anonymous holiday operation. It is a welcoming cabin where hospitality stays human and thoughtful.</p></div></section>

    <section class="section muted"><div class="container"><h2>What Guests Can Expect</h2><div class="grid-3 about-facts-grid">{cabinFacts.map((fact) => <article class="card about-fact-card"><p>{fact}</p></article>)}</div></div></section>

    <section class="section"><div class="container split"><img src={siteConfig.assets.aboutHost} alt="Bush Baby host welcome" loading="lazy" /><div><h2>A Personal Welcome</h2><p>Hello and welcome to Bush Baby. Thank you for considering our cabin for your stay in Sabie. Every enquiry is handled personally, and I’m always happy to help you plan a comfortable visit that suits your group and travel dates.</p><p>I look forward to hosting you with warmth, honesty, and genuine care.</p></div></div></section>

    <section class="section cta-banner"><div class="container"><h2>Have questions before you book?</h2><p>Reach out directly and we’ll guide you through the process step by step.</p><a href="/contact" class="btn btn-primary">Enquire Now</a></div></section>
  </main>
  <Footer />
</BaseLayout>
